# BMad multi-IDE integrations — generated by `bmad-method install`, regenerable,
# personal per-developer tooling for non-Claude IDEs. Claude Code's `.claude/` is
# the committed team toolchain; these other-IDE mirrors are kept out of the repo.
.agents/
.agent/
.opencode/
.github/agents/

